  m_text: "Click on tiles to see their cost and ecological value.\n\nPurchase or
    sell a tile by clicking on the purchase/sell button after selecting a tile.\n\nPurchased
    tiles will add a bonus to the ecological value of tiles nearby if they are not
    already purchased.\n\nClick the submit button  to finish the level.\n\nClick
    the reset to reset all purchased tiles. \n\nHitting the ESC key will open the
    pause menu."
